<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77d364fc-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s460aa–14"><num value="460aa–14">§ 460aa–14.</num><heading> Separability</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">If any provision of this subchapter is declared to be invalid, such declaration shall not affect the validity of any other provision of this subchapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id77d364fd-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/92/400/s15">Pub. L. 92–400, § 15</ref>, <date date="1972-08-22">Aug. 22, 1972</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/86/615">86 Stat. 615</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
